1. *Moć* nam je potrebna da bi obavili ovaj posao. (We need power to do this job.)
2. On je sposoban da stekne *moć*. (He is capable of gaining power.)
3. Oni su već imali *moć*. (They already had power.)
4. On je bio *moćan* čovek. (He was a powerful man.)
5. Oni su hteli da održe svoju *moć*. (They wanted to keep their power.)
6. *Moć* ljudi se razlikuje od jednog do drugog. (People's power varies from one to another.)
7. Ona ima *moć* da promeni stvari. (She has the power to change things.)
8. Oni su se borili za *moć*. (They fought for power.)
9. Ona je osećala *moć* koju je posedovala. (She felt the power she had.)
10. *Moć* je bila njegova opsesija. (Power was his obsession.)